ll><a:latin typeface="Roboto"/><a:ea typeface="Roboto"/><a:cs typeface="Roboto"/><a:sym typeface="Roboto"/></a:rPr><a:t>As a partner, we can get the conversation started with an outline of the courses (excluding any content partner titles) you’d like to bundle, provide a description and bundle name, include projections, and we’ll outline the learner list price once the bundle pricing is approved. We can also discuss your marketing plan.</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:pic><p:nvPicPr><p:cNvPr id="3" name="Picture 2"><a:extLst><a:ext uri="{FF2B5EF4-FFF2-40B4-BE49-F238E27FC236}"><a16:creationId xmlns:a16="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/drawing/2014/main" id="{B9D26A3A-8988-41A8-AA42-461C019FF0CC}"/></a:ext></a:extLst></p:cNvPr><p:cNvPicPr><a:picLocks noChangeAspect="1"/></p:cNvPicPr><p:nvPr/></p:nvPicPr><p:blipFill><a:blip r:embed="rId3"/><a:stretch><a:fillRect/></a:stretch></p:blipFill><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="4146900" y="1099445"/><a:ext cx="3993797" cy="2889130"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom></p:spPr></p:pic></p:spTree><p:extLst><p:ext uri="{BB962C8B-B14F-4D97-AF65-F5344CB8AC3E}"><p14:creationId xmlns:p14="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/powerpoint/2010/main" val="901585940"/></p:ext></p:extLst></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr></p:sld>